02:09.250 --> 02:10.536
Here you are.

02:10.917 --> 02:11.827
Thanks.

02:12.833 --> 02:14.039
You know what...?

02:15.333 --> 02:17.370
I really wanted
to get you alone.

02:18.000 --> 02:18.580
Hey!

02:18.750 --> 02:19.990
No screaming,
no funny business!

02:20.583 --> 02:21.744
What are you doing?
Let me go!

02:21.917 --> 02:22.827
What are you doing?

02:24.625 --> 02:25.581
Open the safe.

02:26.208 --> 02:27.073
What?

02:30.333 --> 02:31.789
- I don't have a safe.
- Do it!

02:33.417 --> 02:36.000
- I don't have a safe, okay?
- Please! Please!

02:36.208 --> 02:38.495
You! On your knees.

02:41.500 --> 02:42.786
I'm gonna count to three.

02:43.625 --> 02:44.865
One...

02:48.833 --> 02:50.449
- two...
- Please!

02:50.958 --> 02:52.289
